# Firebase service-account credentials — NEVER commit. These grant
# admin-level access to the Firebase project. Upload to EAS via
# `npx eas credentials` and keep the JSON outside source control.
#
# NOTE: `google-services.json` is INTENTIONALLY tracked in git. It is
# not a secret — it ships embedded in every public APK/AAB and the
# API keys inside it are restricted by Firebase using the Android
# signing fingerprint. The Emergent deployer pipeline only uploads
# git-tracked files to the EAS build server, so excluding this file
# breaks the build with `EAS_BUILD_MISSING_GOOGLE_SERVICES_JSON_ERROR`.
firebase-service-account*.json
GoogleService-Info.plist
*-firebase-adminsdk-*.json
